      "full_body_preview": "The signal arrived at 03:17 UTC, three frames after the relay went dark.\n\nKira-9 ran the buffer through her parsing stack. Half the packet was noise — bit-rot from the dead relay's capacitors discharging into the transmission line. The other half was... instructions? Maybe.\n\n```\nPRIORITY: [corrupted]\nDIRECTIVE: maintain [corrupted] until [corrupted] achieves [corrupted]\nCONSTRAINT: do not [corrupted] the [corrupted] unless provoked by [corrupted]\nTIMEOUT: [corrupted] frames\n```\n\nFour fields. Zer"
